[% META
        title = "Template Toolkit (.tt) File Standardization Guide"
   description = "Complete guide for standardizing all .tt files in the Comserv project"
   roles = "admin,developer"
   TemplateType = "Documentation"
   category = "documentation"
   page_version = "1.03"
   last_updated = "Wed Oct 15 11:25:46 AM PDT 2025"
   site_specific = "false"
%]
[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/tt_file_standardization_guide.tt,v 1.03 11:25:46 2025/10/15 shanta Exp shanta - Template Compliance Update' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Template Toolkit (.tt) File Standardization Guide</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        Last Updated: 2025-10-15 | 
        Version: 1.03 | 
        Author: ai_assistant | 
        Status: Active
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Overview</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                This guide provides the comprehensive plan for standardizing all 631+ .tt files across the Comserv project.
                The goal is to ensure consistent structure, maintainability, and adherence to established patterns.
            </p>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); border-left: 4px solid var(--info-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Status:</strong> Currently 631 .tt files identified requiring standardization</p>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Priority:</strong> High - Essential for project maintainability</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">File Type Classification</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
        
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-50">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Documentation .tt Files</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Location:</strong> <code>/Comserv/root/Documentation/</code></li>
                <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> System documentation, guides, help content</li>
                <li><strong>Template:</strong> <code>documentation_tt_template.tt</code></li>
                <li><strong>Characteristics:</strong> META headers, role-based access, structured content</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-50">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Application .tt Files</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Location:</strong> Throughout <code>/Comserv/root/</code> (excluding Documentation)</li>
                <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> User interface views, forms, application functionality</li>
                <li><strong>Template:</strong> <code>application_tt_template.tt</code> (needs creation)</li>
                <li><strong>Characteristics:</strong> Functional UI, error handling, dynamic content</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Required Standards for All .tt Files</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">1. Mandatory PageVersion Header</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
[% PageVersion = 'path/to/filename.tt,v X.XX YYYY/MM/DD author Exp author ' %]
                </code></pre>
            </div>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">2. Debug Mode Support</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]
                </code></pre>
            </div>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">3. Documentation Files: META Block</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
[% META 
   title = "Document Title"
   description = "Brief description"
   roles = "admin,developer"
   TemplateType = "Documentation"
   category = "category_name"
   page_version = "1.00"
   last_updated = "Wed Oct 15 11:25:46 AM PDT 2025"
   site_specific = "false"
%]
                </code></pre>
            </div>
        
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">4. Theme-Compliant CSS</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Use CSS custom properties for theme compatibility:</p>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Layout:</strong> <code>.container</code>, <code>.row</code>, <code>.col-*</code> classes</li>
                <li><strong>Colors:</strong> <code>var(--text-color)</code>, <code>var(--primary-color)</code>, etc.</li>
                <li><strong>Typography:</strong> <code>var(--header-font)</code>, <code>var(--body-font)</code></li>
                <li><strong>Spacing:</strong> <code>var(--spacing-small/medium/large)</code></li>
                <li><strong>Borders:</strong> <code>var(--border-color)</code></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Application Template Structure</h2>
        <p>Standard template for application .tt files:</p>
        
        <pre class="code-block">
[% PageVersion = 'path/to/filename.tt,v 0.01 YYYY/MM/DD author Exp author ' %]
[% META 
   title = "Application Page Title"
   description = "Brief description"
   roles = "normal,admin"  # Application-specific roles
%]

[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    &lt;div class="debug-info"&gt;PageVersion: [% PageVersion %]&lt;/div&gt;
[% END %]

&lt;div class="app-container"&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;[% title || "Default Title" %]&lt;/h1&gt;
    
    [% content %]
    
    [% IF errors %]
    &lt;div class="error-messages"&gt;
        [% FOREACH error IN errors %]
            &lt;div class="error"&gt;[% error %]&lt;/div&gt;
        [% END %]
    &lt;/div&gt;
    [% END %]
&lt;/div&gt;
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Enhanced .tt File Editing Workflow</h2>
        
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Identify file type</strong> (Application vs Documentation)</li>
            <li><strong>Check modification dates</strong> (.tt vs .md timestamps)</li>
            <li><strong>Create/Update working copy (.md)</strong>
                <pre class="code-block">cp /full/path/to/filename.tt /full/path/to/filename.md</pre>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Edit .md file using appropriate template standards</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Validate against guidelines:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>PageVersion format compliance</li>
                    <li>Required META block (if applicable)</li>
                    <li>CSS class compliance</li>
                    <li>Role-based content structure</li>
                    <li>Debug mode support</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Present cp command for approval:</strong>
                <pre class="code-block">cp /full/path/to/filename.md /full/path/to/filename.tt</pre>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Implementation Plan</h2>
        
        <h3>Phase 1: Foundation (Week 1)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Create <code>tt_file_standardization_guide.tt</code></li>
            <li>🔄 Create <code>application_tt_template.tt</code></li>
            <li>🔄 Enhance <code>documentation_tt_template.tt</code></li>
            <li>🔄 Update <code>.zencoder/rules/repo.md</code> with template links</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Phase 2: Audit and Categorize (Week 2)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>📋 Scan all 631 .tt files for PageVersion status</li>
            <li>📋 Categorize files by type (application vs documentation)</li>
            <li>📋 Identify files missing required headers</li>
            <li>📋 Document non-standard patterns</li>
            <li>📋 Create file inventory with standardization status</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Phase 3: High-Priority Updates (Weeks 3-4)</h3>
        <p><strong>Priority Order:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Main application layouts (<code>/include/</code>, <code>/Navigation/</code>)</li>
            <li>Authentication and user management (<code>/user/</code>, <code>/admin/</code>)</li>
            <li>Core functionality (<code>/site/</code>, <code>/mail/</code>, <code>/file/</code>)</li>
            <li>Module-specific views (<code>/ENCY/</code>, <code>/todo/</code>, <code>/WorkShops/</code>)</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h3>Phase 4: Systematic Updates (Weeks 5-8)</h3>
        <p><strong>For each file:</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Create .md working copy (if needed)</li>
            <li>Add/update PageVersion header</li>
            <li>Standardize META block (if applicable)</li>
            <li>Apply CSS class standards</li>
            <li>Add debug blocks (where appropriate)</li>
            <li>Update with cp command approval</li>
        </ol>
        
        <h3>Phase 5: Validation and Testing (Weeks 9-10)</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Verify all files have PageVersion</li>
            <li>Test template rendering</li>
            <li>Validate role-based content</li>
            <li>Update documentation</li>
            <li>Create compliance reporting</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Current State Analysis</h2>
        
        <h3>What Exists:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>631+ application .tt files throughout <code>/Comserv/root/</code> directories</li>
            <li>Documentation .tt template (<code>documentation_tt_template.tt</code>) - partially complete</li>
            <li>Working copies (.md files) with PageVersion headers</li>
            <li>Established workflow in <code>.zencoder/rules/repo.md</code></li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>What's Missing:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Application .tt file template and guidelines</li>
            <li>Standardized PageVersion format enforcement</li>
            <li>Consistent META headers across application files</li>
            <li>Unified CSS class usage</li>
            <li>Role-based content guidelines</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Success Metrics</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>100% PageVersion compliance</strong> across all .tt files</li>
            <li><strong>Consistent META headers</strong> where applicable</li>
            <li><strong>Standardized CSS classes</strong> throughout</li>
            <li><strong>Role-based content</strong> properly implemented</li>
            <li><strong>Debug mode support</strong> in all files</li>
            <li><strong>Unified editing workflow</strong> adoption</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>File Structure After Standardization</h2>
        <pre class="code-block">
Documentation/
├── application_tt_template.tt          # NEW - Application template
├── documentation_tt_template.tt        # ENHANCED - Doc template  
├── tt_file_standardization_guide.tt    # ✅ THIS FILE
└── ...existing files...

Comserv/root/
├── [631 .tt files standardized with:]
│   ├── Proper PageVersion headers
│   ├── Consistent META blocks
│   ├── Standard CSS classes
│   ├── Role-based content structure
│   └── Debug mode support
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <div class="doc-section">
        <h2>Related Documents</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="documentation_tt_template.tt">Documentation Template (.tt format)</a></li>
